; Name ..........: BreakPersonalShield
; Description ...: Function to break shield and personal guard
; Syntax ........: BreakPersonalShield()
; Parameters ....: none
; Return values .: none
; ...............: Sets @error if buttons not found properly and sets @extended with string error message
